description: Aspose.Imaging for .NET is an imaging library that lets developers create, edit, draw or convert images in their .NET applications. Aspose.Imaging provides features that go beyond the native capabilities of the development platform. It works independent of other applications and although Aspose.Imaging allows you to save to Adobe PhotoShop® format (PSD), you do not need PhotoShop on the machine.
releaseNotes:
New Features

IMAGING-31743	Supported concatenate of Tiff Images 
IMAGING-33119	Supported Image export to Tiff with compression 
IMAGING-31979	Supported loading of multi-page TIFF files 
IMAGING-33142	Supported export to CCIT RLE compressed Tiff 
IMAGING-33141	Supported export to uncompressed Tiff 
IMAGING-33185	Supported CCIT4 compression 
IMAGING-33184	Supported CCIT3 compression 
IMAGING-33193	Ability to save each frame of Tiff to different image format
 
Enhancements 
IMAGING-33158	Improve Imaging performance
